      "body" : "Indeed this is the drawback, which would mean I better remove the fancy utf-8 chars as well...\r\n\r\nObviously we are running the daemons on different ports, so within the test framework it is more than unlikely to accidentally speak to the wrong daemon. I think a reasonable compromise would be to use `'rt_u'+str(n)` and `'rt_p'+str(n)`.",
